::Zardus::

Zardus looks up from Squizzy as Cybershark comes in. "Ah, yes.." he says in 
reply to the bot's request, "I may have a mission for you. But first, go into 
one of the CR chambers. You have been in the Cybertronian Fire, and have some 
info that I might need. The CR chamber will automatically download it, and 
then I'll give you the mission."

He glances back at the other console, with Squizzy's old main proccessor, to 
see if it had gotten anywhere yet.
